 what is\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":40167,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/05\/18\/usri-yusrayn\/","url_meta":{"origin":24620,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Ease: Difficulty decreed along with two reliefs","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 18, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Qatadah ibn Di\u2019amatah reported: It has been mentioned to us that the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, gave glad tidings to his companions about this verse, \u201cVerily, with the hardship comes an ease, with the hardship comes an ease,\u201d (94:5-6) and the Prophet said, \u201cA hardship\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33705,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/10\/13\/dhikr-wonder-creation\/","url_meta":{"origin":24620,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Dhikr: Observing nature\u2019s wonders to remember Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 13, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abi Awfa reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, among the best servants of Allah are those who observe the sun, the moon, the stars, and the shades for the remembrance of Allah.\u201d Source: al-Sunan al-Kubra\u0301 lil-Bayhaqi\u0304 170 Grade: Hasan li ghayrihi (fair\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"te